  "inscription": "(excerpt)<br />  Many of the objects in this installation were found rummaging through discarded items from the airport's workspaces that include Building Maintenance, Electrical, Welding, and Sign shops.  <br />  Woolford created <i>Love Awaits You</i> to \"enchant travelers landing at the airport and for loved ones Who wait for their arrival.\"  He said, \"the plane flying towards the big HRT encompasses that  total experience.\"",
